{"id":"gARE8J9JaOY2pIaI","meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":true},"name":"AI Image Generation → Supabase Storage","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"demo-video-note-image","name":"🎥 Demo Video","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-944,-20],"parameters":{"width":480,"height":380,"content":"## 🎥 Watch the demo\n\n@[youtube](KWcSUUUuV74)\n\nBuilt by **Aumadi** — pj@aumadi.com"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"b3d12f71-0618-4a6e-8ab2-6976f03008a4","name":"📘 Overview","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-944,440],"parameters":{"width":470,"height":320,"content":"## 🖼️ AI Image Generation → Supabase Storage\n\n### Who's it for\nBuilders who want an automated image pipeline: drop an idea into a database row and get back a finished image with a public URL — no manual steps.\n\n### How it works\n1. A new row in the `image_jobs` table (Supabase Database Webhook) starts the flow.\n2. **Claude** turns the raw idea into a rich image prompt.\n3. **Cloudflare Workers AI (FLUX · free)** generates the image.\n4. The image is uploaded to **Supabase Storage**.\n5. The public URL + a `done` status are written back to the row.\n\n### Requirements\n- Supabase project (Database + Storage)\n- Anthropic API key (Claude)\n- Cloudflare account + Workers AI token\n\n*All Supabase nodes use ONE Supabase credential; only the **⚙️ Config** node holds your project URL + bucket.*"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"4bd6e68b-aded-4b2a-b240-f78d75604ef8","name":"🔧 Setup","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-944,800],"parameters":{"width":470,"height":320,"content":"## 🔧 Setup\n1. Run `new-workflows-setup.sql` (creates `image_jobs`).\n2. Storage → New bucket → **generated-images** → Public ON.\n3. Credentials:\n   - **Claude (Anthropic)** → Header Auth, name `x-api-key`, value = your Anthropic key.\n   - **Cloudflare Workers AI** → Header Auth, name `Authorization`, value `Bearer YOUR_CF_TOKEN` (free). Set your account id in the image node URL.\n   - **Supabase** → host = your project URL, service_role key.\n4. In the **⚙️ Config** node, set `supabaseUrl` to your project URL.\n5. Supabase → Database → Webhooks → table `image_jobs`, event Insert, POST → `https://YOUR_N8N_URL/webhook/generate-image`\n6. Activate. Test: insert a row with a `prompt`."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"8cbc74fb-98aa-47a9-ab47-2830e88f8597","name":"New Image Job (Insert)","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","position":[-432,464],"webhookId":"generate-image","parameters":{"path":"generate-image","options":{},"httpMethod":"POST","responseMode":"responseNode"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"d5459726-f2cd-4b2e-b17c-9baf54282909","name":"⚙️ Config","type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","position":[-208,464],"parameters":{"options":{},"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"c_url","name":"supabaseUrl","type":"string","value":"https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co"},{"id":"c_bucket","name":"bucket","type":"string","value":"generated-images"},{"id":"c_tmodel","name":"textModel","type":"string","value":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001"}]}},"typeVersion":3.4},{"id":"df473f5c-e840-436e-a6c5-a902b7a13529","name":"Parse Job","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[16,464],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Read the Supabase Database Webhook payload (insert on image_jobs).\nconst input = $('New Image Job (Insert)').first().json;\nconst body = input.body || input;\nconst rec = body.record || body;\nreturn [{ json: { jobId: rec.id, prompt: String(rec.prompt || '').trim() } }];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"cae7f549-4171-4925-a17e-19ad02b11955","name":"Has a prompt?","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[240,464],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"version":2,"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":true,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"c_has","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty","singleValue":true},"leftValue":"={{ $json.prompt }}","rightValue":""}]}},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"bf4e16d7-f032-4925-8728-75d59fb5460c","name":"Skip (no prompt)","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","position":[464,688],"parameters":{"options":{},"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ JSON.stringify({ skipped: true, reason: 'no prompt' }) }}"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"4cfe5247-6361-475e-86d5-251718a1ea8e","name":"🧠 Claude: Enhance Prompt","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","onError":"continueErrorOutput","position":[464,464],"parameters":{"url":"https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages","method":"POST","options":{"timeout":30000},"jsonBody":"={{ JSON.stringify({ model: $('⚙️ Config').first().json.textModel, max_tokens: 300, system: 'You turn a short idea into ONE vivid, detailed image-generation prompt — subject, style, lighting, mood, composition. Output ONLY the prompt, no preamble.', messages: [ { role: 'user', content: 'Idea: ' + $('Parse Job').first().json.prompt } ] }) }}","sendBody":true,"sendHeaders":true,"specifyBody":"json","authentication":"genericCredentialType","genericAuthType":"httpHeaderAuth","headerParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"anthropic-version","value":"2023-06-01"},{"name":"content-type","value":"application/json"}]}},"credentials":{"httpHeaderAuth":{"id":"REPLACE_ANTHROPIC_CRED","name":"anthropic"}},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"5e88a4e8-e33e-4ae7-84b7-481413699ff9","name":"Extract Prompt","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[688,464],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Handles both Claude (r.content[].text) and Gemini (r.candidates[0].content.parts[].text).\nconst r = $input.first().json;\nlet t = '';\ntry {\n  if (Array.isArray(r.content)) { t = r.content.map(c => c.text || '').join(' ').trim(); }\n  else if (r.candidates) { t = (r.candidates[0].content.parts || []).map(p => p.text || '').join(' ').trim(); }\n} catch (e) {}\nconst fallback = $('Parse Job').first().json.prompt;\nreturn [{ json: { imagePrompt: t || fallback } }];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"c3a8cab1-0bbe-4934-9f18-a5b11abc2589","name":"Image → Binary","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[1120,464],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// Cloudflare FLUX returns the image as base64 in result.image (JPEG).\nconst r = $input.first().json;\nconst b64 = (r && r.result && r.result.image) ? r.result.image : '';\nif (!b64) { throw new Error('No image in response'); }\nreturn [{ json: {}, binary: { data: { data: b64, mimeType: 'image/jpeg', fileName: 'image.jpg' } } }];\n"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"e7790c5e-3c03-4bc2-9237-d70e44a47460","name":"☁️ Upload to Supabase Storage","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","onError":"continueErrorOutput","position":[1344,464],"parameters":{"url":"={{ $('⚙️ Config').first().json.supabaseUrl }}/storage/v1/object/{{ $('⚙️ Config').first().json.bucket }}/{{ $('Parse Job').first().json.jobId }}.png","method":"POST","options":{"timeout":30000},"sendBody":true,"contentType":"binaryData","sendHeaders":true,"authentication":"predefinedCredentialType","headerParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"Content-Type","value":"image/png"},{"name":"x-upsert","value":"true"}]},"inputDataFieldName":"data","nodeCredentialType":"supabaseApi"},"credentials":{"supabaseApi":{"id":"REPLACE_SUPABASE_CRED","name":"Supabase account"}},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"c68db8ff-1927-4625-b808-b642c3e521a8","name":"Build Public URL","type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","position":[1568,464],"parameters":{"options":{},"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"u_url","name":"imageUrl","type":"string","value":"={{ $('⚙️ Config').first().json.supabaseUrl }}/storage/v1/object/public/{{ $('⚙️ Config').first().json.bucket }}/{{ $('Parse Job').first().json.jobId }}.png"}]}},"typeVersion":3.4},{"id":"042db26d-1bd2-4b4b-940d-0c83af96b07b","name":"Update Job → done","type":"n8n-nodes-base.supabase","position":[1776,464],"parameters":{"filters":{"conditions":[{"keyName":"id","keyValue":"={{ $('Parse Job').first().json.jobId }}","condition":"eq"}]},"tableId":"image_jobs","fieldsUi":{"fieldValues":[{"fieldId":"status","fieldValue":"done"},{"fieldId":"image_url","fieldValue":"={{ $json.imageUrl }}"}]},"operation":"update"},"credentials":{"supabaseApi":{"id":"REPLACE_SUPABASE_CRED","name":"Supabase account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c6bb9715-0d79-4f29-9cbf-129fe02136e2","name":"200 Done","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","position":[2000,464],"parameters":{"options":{},"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ JSON.stringify({ status: 'done', imageUrl: $json.image_url || $('Build Public URL').first().json.imageUrl }) }}"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"070eaae3-e284-400a-b3cb-c44d961fd5b7","name":"Update Job → error","type":"n8n-nodes-base.supabase","position":[1120,736],"parameters":{"filters":{"conditions":[{"keyName":"id","keyValue":"={{ $('Parse Job').first().json.jobId }}","condition":"eq"}]},"tableId":"image_jobs","fieldsUi":{"fieldValues":[{"fieldId":"status","fieldValue":"error"},{"fieldId":"error_message","fieldValue":"={{ ($json.error && $json.error.message) || 'image generation/upload failed' }}"}]},"operation":"update"},"credentials":{"supabaseApi":{"id":"REPLACE_SUPABASE_CRED","name":"Supabase account"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"004eaf4c-9b3d-40ca-9b46-932998d764ac","name":"500 Error","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","position":[1344,736],"parameters":{"options":{"responseCode":500},"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ JSON.stringify({ status: 'error' }) }}"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"8e82d083-08f4-4ffe-b067-ea709a3f6bf0","name":"🎨cloudflare Image","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","onError":"continueErrorOutput","position":[896,464],"parameters":{"url":"=https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/YOUR_CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID/ai/run/@cf/black-forest-labs/flux-1-schnell","method":"POST","options":{"timeout":60000},"jsonBody":"={{ JSON.stringify({ prompt: $json.imagePrompt, steps: 4 }) }}\n","sendBody":true,"specifyBody":"json","authentication":"genericCredentialType","genericAuthType":"httpHeaderAuth"},"credentials":{"httpHeaderAuth":{"id":"REPLACE_CLOUDFLARE_CRED","name":"Cloudflare Workers AI"}},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"sec-trigger-img","name":"Section — Trigger & validate","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-460,380],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":860,"height":240,"content":"## ① Trigger & validate\n\nA Supabase **Database Webhook** fires when a new row is inserted into `image_jobs`. **⚙️ Config** holds your project URL + bucket, **Parse Job** reads the new row's `prompt`, and **Has a prompt?** filters out empty rows."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"sec-ai-img","name":"Section — AI prompt & image","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[420,380],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":880,"height":240,"content":"## ② AI — prompt & image\n\n**Claude** turns the raw idea into a rich image prompt. **Extract Prompt** cleans the reply, then **Cloudflare Workers AI (FLUX)** generates the image and **Image → Binary** decodes the base64 into a file."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"sec-store-img","name":"Section — Store & finish","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1310,380],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":900,"height":240,"content":"## ③ Store image & finish\n\nThe image is uploaded to **Supabase Storage**, **Build Public URL** assembles its public link, **Update Job → done** writes the URL + `done` status back to the row, and **200 Done** returns the result."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"sec-error-img","name":"Section — Skip & errors","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[420,640],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":1180,"height":240,"content":"## ④ Skip & error handling\n\nRows with no prompt return **Skip (no prompt)**. If Claude, Cloudflare, or the upload fail, **Update Job → error** records the message on the row and **500 Error** responds — so no job is left silently stuck."},"typeVersion":1}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"binaryMode":"separate","executionOrder":"v1"},"versionId":"7d5e604d-6407-4825-848a-0e6fa2dd1a5a","connections":{"Parse Job":{"main":[[{"node":"Has a prompt?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Has a prompt?":{"main":[[{"node":"🧠 Claude: Enhance Prompt","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Skip (no prompt)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"⚙️ Config":{"main":[[{"node":"Parse Job","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract Prompt":{"main":[[{"node":"🎨cloudflare Image","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Build Public URL":{"main":[[{"node":"Update Job → done","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Image → Binary":{"main":[[{"node":"☁️ Upload to Supabase Storage","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Job → done":{"main":[[{"node":"200 Done","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Job → error":{"main":[[{"node":"500 Error","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🎨cloudflare Image":{"main":[[{"node":"Image → Binary","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Update Job → error","type":"main","index":0}]]},"New Image Job (Insert)":{"main":[[{"node":"⚙️ Config","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🧠 Claude: Enhance Prompt":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Prompt","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Update Job → error","type":"main","index":0}]]},"☁️ Upload to Supabase Storage":{"main":[[{"node":"Build Public URL","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Update Job → error","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}